Lighter version of https://github.com/globality-corp/microcosm-pubsub/pull/85

Simple method decorator that produces (sns) messages. Supports some customization.

Simple example:
```
        @publish(
             media_type=created(company),
             uri=lambda component, model: f"/api/v1/company/{model.id}"
        )
        def create(**kwargs):
            return company(id="ID")
        produce:
            application/vnd.globality.pubsub._.created.company message
            with: {'uri': '/api/v1/company/ID'}
```

